Jamie Richardson and Daniel Taylor fined $3,000 for threatening behaviour on flight from London to Mexico . 
  Pair pleaded guilty to using threatening behaviour in a Bermuda court . 
  Richardson allegedly threw peanuts and a pound coin at cabin crew . 
  Taylor accused of hitting himself on the head with clenched fists . 
  Flight forced to divert to Bermuda and could face four-month jail term . 
 